'''Merisee Prime Pharmaceutical''' was a company which used the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Meris III]]'s unusual fauna as a basis for most of its drugs. The drug company's headquarters was located in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Caronath]] on the planet [[Merisee/Legends|Merisee]].

